When a remore user directory is synchronizing, you get the foolowing message in the logs:
{quote}synchroniseCache synchronisation for directory [ 1234567 ] starting{quote}

When the synchronization is done, it is also reflected in the logs as:
{quote}synchroniseCache FULL synchronisation complete in [ 32185ms ]{quote}

