This is very confusing for users who would expect to use multiple SMTP servers as a fail over.

Olivier Beg <olivier@hotmail.lv> reported
{quote}
{noformat}https://confluence.atlassian.com/dosearchsite.action?queryString=%22%3E&startIndex=0&lastModified=LASTWEEK&where=conf_all%22%3E%3Cimg%20src=x%20onerror=alert(1)%3E{noformat}

> I asume he is DOM based because he works in google chrome.
{quote}

This results in 

{code:html}
  <input type="hidden" id="search-filter-by-space" name="where" value="conf_all&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=x onerror=alert(1)&gt;" style="width: 100%"/>
{code}

